title: sleep deprivation
comment: This deprivation could be externally-led or may come from people's own desires to "get ahead" in some way.

title: social stigmatisation
comment: Some people will take a dim view of this as "playing god" or interfering with nature and so may ostracise those that choose to have the implant

title: employer pressure
comment: Pressure may come in the form of getting the implant and also regulation of the sleep patterns that a person must use.
